### Stock Market Simulator API - HTTP Requests
### This file contains all API endpoints for testing with REST Client or similar tools
### Set @token = your_jwt_token_here after logging in

@token = 

### 
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### 

### Register a new user account
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "trader_john",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

### Login to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

### Get current user profile
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update user profile
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "trader_john_updated",
  "profilePicture": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### Get all users (admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 
### STOCK ENDPOINTS
### 

### Get trending/top stocks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stocks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get detailed information about a specific stock
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stocks/INFY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get price history for a stock (last 30 days)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stocks/history/INFY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search for stocks by name or symbol
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stocks/search?q=infosys
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get batch quotes for multiple stocks
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stocks/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbols": ["INFY", "TCS", "WIPRO", "RELIANCE"]
}

### 
### TRADING ENDPOINTS
### 

### Buy stock - Place a buy order
POST http://localhost:5000/api/trade/buy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "INFY",
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 1650.50
}

### Sell stock - Place a sell order
POST http://localhost:5000/api/trade/sell
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "INFY",
  "quantity": 5,
  "price": 1700.75
}

### Get all trades/transaction history
GET http://localhost:5000/api/trade/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 
### PORTFOLIO ENDPOINTS
### 

### Get user's complete portfolio (all holdings)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/portfolio
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get profit & loss summary for portfolio
GET http://localhost:5000/api/portfolio/profit-loss
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get portfolio summary with statistics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/portfolio/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 
### WALLET ENDPOINTS
### 

### Check current wallet balance
GET http://localhost:5000/api/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add funds to wallet (deposit)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/wallet/add-funds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000
}

### Withdraw funds from wallet
POST http://localhost:5000/api/wallet/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2000
}

### Get wallet transaction history
GET http://localhost:5000/api/wallet/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 
### WATCHLIST ENDPOINTS
### 

### Get user's watchlist
GET http://localhost:5000/api/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add stock to watchlist
POST http://localhost:5000/api/watchlist/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "TCS"
}

### Remove stock from watchlist
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/watchlist/remove
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "TCS"
}

### 
### ALERT ENDPOINTS
### 

### Create price alert for a stock
POST http://localhost:5000/api/alerts/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "INFY",
  "alertType": "price_above",
  "targetPrice": 1750,
  "condition": "greater_than"
}

### Get all alerts for user
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete an alert
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/alerts/delete/64a9c8f2b1d2e3f4a5b6c7d8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 
### LEADERBOARD ENDPOINTS
### 

### Get global leaderboard (top traders by portfolio value)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaderboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get monthly leaderboard (top gainers this month)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaderboard?period=monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get user's leaderboard rank
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaderboard/rank
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 
### HEALTH CHECK
### 

### Check API health status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### Get API info and available endpoints
GET http://localhost:5000

### 
### SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
### 
### 
### 1. Install REST Client extension in VS Code
### 2. Start your backend server: npm run dev
### 3. Register a new user or login with existing credentials
### 4. Copy the JWT token from the response
### 5. Replace @token value at the top of this file with your JWT token
### 6. Run requests by clicking "Send Request" link that appears above each request
###
### Environment: Development (local)
### Port: 5000 (adjust if different in your setup)
### Database: MongoDB (ensure it's running)
###
